<p>Find <m>a</m> and <m>b</m> so that the exponential growth model <m>y = a b^x</m> contains the points <m>$p1</m> and <m>$p2m</m>.</p>

<p><em>Round your answers to the nearest <m>0.001</m></em>.</p>


